Make everything gone in one bang,

794
01:06:17,125 --> 01:06:19,500
so we don't have to do it many times.

795
01:06:21,208 --> 01:06:24,208
It's done. One-shot kill.

796
01:06:24,500 --> 01:06:26,958
There was a flash and then he fell.

797
01:06:28,875 --> 01:06:32,250
Excellent! This is how I like it.

798
01:06:34,750 --> 01:06:37,083
But the way you dress

799
01:06:37,250 --> 01:06:39,041
is as bad as those three dumb shits.

800
01:06:55,208 --> 01:06:57,833
What a miracle.

801
01:06:59,333 --> 01:07:00,791
There's a hole in the alms bowl,

802
01:07:01,583 --> 01:07:03,166
but Brother Joey is fine.

803
01:07:04,291 --> 01:07:06,583
This is the same story

804
01:07:07,125 --> 01:07:10,375
as with Grandfather's first disciple.

805
01:07:13,000 --> 01:07:15,833
I told you many times

806
01:07:17,583 --> 01:07:20,125
but nobody listened.

807
01:07:21,541 --> 01:07:25,708
I said don't bother with them.

808
01:07:27,375 --> 01:07:30,708
But why? You misheard me?

809
01:07:31,625 --> 01:07:33,416
Why didn't you do as I said?

810
01:07:38,416 --> 01:07:40,958
Let's go.

811
01:07:48,666 --> 01:07:51,291
How did you end up here?
Is it not difficult?

812
01:07:54,000 --> 01:07:57,250
As long as we have Dharma
in our hearts,

813
01:07:58,500 --> 01:08:00,250
it's not difficult anywhere.

814
01:08:01,416 --> 01:08:03,625
Dharma is nature

815
01:08:04,291 --> 01:08:06,833
that clears our minds.

816
01:08:08,875 --> 01:08:10,125
And some people

817
01:08:11,625 --> 01:08:13,291
who live in civilized places,

818
01:08:14,500 --> 01:08:17,500
their minds are not as civilized.
That's not good.

819
01:08:18,625 --> 01:08:21,375
Did you have a family before?

820
01:08:24,167 --> 01:08:27,082
Yes, I did.

821
01:08:28,292 --> 01:08:29,457
But then...

822
01:08:30,457 --> 01:08:33,000
when we saw things
we used to dream of,

823
01:08:34,042 --> 01:08:36,792
it became a light

824
01:08:37,667 --> 01:08:41,332
that made me decide to give something up

825
01:08:41,707 --> 01:08:43,250
and come live here.

826
01:09:01,332 --> 01:09:03,332
Brother!

827
01:09:04,332 --> 01:09:05,332
Brother.

828
01:09:06,957 --> 01:09:09,457
Brother! Grandfather's coughing blood.

829
01:09:13,167 --> 01:09:14,582
Prepare the car.

830
01:09:15,957 --> 01:09:18,082
-Hurry.
-Hurry up.

831
01:09:18,707 --> 01:09:20,375
-Let's go.
-Hurry.

832
01:09:23,875 --> 01:09:25,500
Hurry up!

833
01:09:25,625 --> 01:09:27,542
Wait up!

834
01:09:29,542 --> 01:09:30,542
Hey!

835
01:09:31,917 --> 01:09:32,792
Hey!

836
01:09:35,042 --> 01:09:35,917
Wait!

837
01:09:42,832 --> 01:09:45,582
Stay strong, Grandfather.
We're almost there.

838
01:09:48,582 --> 01:09:49,625
Stay strong.

839
01:09:49,832 --> 01:09:50,707
Wait.

840
01:09:51,457 --> 01:09:53,332
Just a little bit further.

841
01:09:59,625 --> 01:10:01,457
What's with all this, Lord Buddha?

842
01:10:03,750 --> 01:10:05,625
What's wrong with the monks
in this temple?

843
01:10:29,000 --> 01:10:30,542
Grandfather.

844
01:10:32,082 --> 01:10:33,000
Just a bit further.

845
01:10:35,417 --> 01:10:38,292
-Let's go heal at the temple.
-Let's go forward.

846
01:10:38,500 --> 01:10:39,875
Just a bit.

847
01:10:46,292 --> 01:10:47,917
Let go with your hand.

848
01:11:05,250 --> 01:11:06,500
PUBLIC HEALTH CENTER

849
01:11:08,375 --> 01:11:10,542
-Hurry!
-Hurry up!

850
01:11:10,792 --> 01:11:12,125
-Hurry!
-Quick, quick.

851
01:11:12,207 --> 01:11:14,125
-Grandfather.
-Hurry!

852
01:11:14,417 --> 01:11:17,417
-Quick.
-Why didn't you help?

853
01:11:17,582 --> 01:11:20,000
Letting Brother carry Grandfather alone.

854
01:11:20,167 --> 01:11:23,250
Why did you open the back?
Grandfather is already on the ground.

855
01:11:23,542 --> 01:11:25,625
-Close it up.
-Help, hurry!

856
01:11:26,375 --> 01:11:28,042
Hurry up!

857
01:11:30,500 --> 01:11:31,832
Come inside.

858
01:11:31,917 --> 01:11:34,292
Please go to the room.

859
01:11:41,542 --> 01:11:44,707
Brother, please wait outside.
You can't be inside.

860
01:11:44,832 --> 01:11:47,332
A little later
and Grandfather wouldn't make it.

861
01:11:50,250 --> 01:11:52,792
A little faster and I wouldn't make it.

862
01:11:53,000 --> 01:11:54,707
You can't be here.

863
01:11:58,875 --> 01:12:00,500
Is it full?

864
01:12:00,582 --> 01:12:03,375
You let Grandfather cough
until his throat is sore?

865
01:12:03,500 --> 01:12:05,207
They won't let us in.

866
01:12:05,332 --> 01:12:07,707
Good thing we had the car.

867
01:12:07,957 --> 01:12:10,042
If not, we would have had to carry him.

868
01:12:11,042 --> 01:12:12,707
Good thing I fixed it.

869
01:12:13,042 --> 01:12:13,917
Doctor.

870
01:12:15,000 --> 01:12:16,625
Mr. Jumlong passed away.

871
01:12:18,457 --> 01:12:19,332
Jumlong!

872
01:12:20,750 --> 01:12:21,875
-Miss Woranuch.
-Yes?

873
01:12:22,000 --> 01:12:25,082
-Take the deceased to the morgue.
-We're about to get engaged.

874
01:12:25,292 --> 01:12:26,957
Don't be so sad.

875
01:12:27,042 --> 01:12:29,917
-We're the same.
-Jumlong!

876
01:12:30,125 --> 01:12:31,750
Don't be sad.

877
01:12:32,542 --> 01:12:34,707
Jumlong, don't leave me.

878
01:12:34,832 --> 01:12:37,417
-We're to be engaged in a few days.
-Make way.

879
01:12:37,500 --> 01:12:39,250
-Jumlong!
-Jumlong.

880
01:12:39,332 --> 01:12:40,917
Why did you leave me?

881
01:12:41,000 --> 01:12:43,542
-Jumlong is dead?
-Jumlong is dead.

882
01:12:43,707 --> 01:12:46,292
Ever since he was born, he just died

883
01:12:46,417 --> 01:12:47,792
-for the first time.
-Brother.

884
01:12:47,917 --> 01:12:49,832
Grandfather needs the respirator.

885
01:12:50,000 --> 01:12:52,500
-Move him to that bed.
-Okay.

886
01:12:55,332 --> 01:12:56,542
Let's go.

887
01:12:56,667 --> 01:12:59,375
Doc, but the guy just died.

888
01:12:59,457 --> 01:13:01,875
-It's okay, they always die on this bed.
-Hey.

889
01:13:02,957 --> 01:13:06,167
-Is it a good idea?
-Birth, old age, sickness, and death.

890
01:13:06,292 --> 01:13:07,667
It's normal.

891
01:13:07,750 --> 01:13:11,125
-What are you talking about?
-Brother, I can't hold on.

892
01:13:13,292 --> 01:13:15,125
Brother, hold him.

893
01:13:18,957 --> 01:13:20,375
Put him in position.

894
01:13:21,582 --> 01:13:24,792
Please open your mouth.

895
01:13:25,457 --> 01:13:27,667
You need the respirator.

896
01:13:28,375 --> 01:13:30,332
Let me check the machine for a bit.

897
01:13:31,957 --> 01:13:35,000
Please let go of it.

898
01:13:37,042 --> 01:13:39,542
Grandfather, please let it go.

899
01:13:40,417 --> 01:13:42,707
Please let go.

900
01:13:43,582 --> 01:13:46,582
Sorry, my hand slipped.

901
01:13:46,917 --> 01:13:49,417
It's okay now. Please breathe.

902
01:13:51,542 --> 01:13:53,957
-Dust from the explosion...
-Do you have Grandfather's

903
01:13:54,082 --> 01:13:55,792
credentials or documents?

904
01:13:55,875 --> 01:13:58,000
Wait until everyone dies?

905
01:13:58,457 --> 01:14:00,417
Brother, Grandfather's credentials.

906
01:14:00,832 --> 01:14:03,042
When will there be a brave man

907
01:14:03,167 --> 01:14:05,750
who goes against that stone mill?

908
01:14:48,667 --> 01:14:49,667
Brother.

909
01:14:53,542 --> 01:14:54,750
I'm a nice man.

910
01:14:56,125 --> 01:14:57,417
I like to help good people.

911
01:14:59,042 --> 01:15:00,707
If I have to be a bad man,

912
01:15:02,707 --> 01:15:04,542
it's to fight bad people.

913
01:15:09,082 --> 01:15:11,917
Put more dynamite in,
make it a big bang.

914
01:15:12,042 --> 01:15:15,667
Make the whole mountain go up
so we don't have to do it many times.

915
01:15:16,417 --> 01:15:17,375
Let's go.

916
01:15:22,957 --> 01:15:24,750
What is it?

917
01:15:29,667 --> 01:15:31,957
Do it again. I won't pay you for this.

918
01:15:59,667 --> 01:16:02,457
Boss, I want to ask for alms.

919
01:16:03,750 --> 01:16:04,957
Can you please stop bombing?

920
01:16:05,792 --> 01:16:07,875
I have instructions.
I'd have to ask Luang.

921
01:16:08,582 --> 01:16:11,207
The dynamite's almost expired.

922
01:16:11,457 --> 01:16:13,250
And I cannot

923
01:16:13,375 --> 01:16:16,082
move the mountain to
be exploded elsewhere.

924
01:16:16,542 --> 01:16:17,582
I think you all

925
01:16:17,707 --> 01:16:20,875
should move away from here.
It's easier.

926
01:16:21,875 --> 01:16:25,167
I say this not out of my selfishness,

927
01:16:25,417 --> 01:16:27,292
but because the temple and village

928
01:16:27,375 --> 01:16:29,917
were here a long time
before my stone mill opened.

929
01:16:30,250 --> 01:16:32,500
And just like that,
now you should move.

930
01:17:20,832 --> 01:17:24,457
It's a good thing I was ordained
in a Thai temple.

931
01:17:27,167 --> 01:17:28,332
Saying it like that,

932
01:17:29,167 --> 01:17:32,167
-you'd blow me up as well.
-You said it yourself.

933
01:17:32,792 --> 01:17:35,750
Fine. Encountering an immoral being,

934
01:17:35,875 --> 01:17:37,625
I'm prepared to die.

935
01:17:38,000 --> 01:17:40,082
Everyone was born to die one day.

936
01:17:40,542 --> 01:17:43,457
Live here any longer, you'll die anyway.
Let's die today.

937
01:17:43,542 --> 01:17:44,792
Let's get it over with.

938
01:17:45,167 --> 01:17:47,625
You said it yourself.
If you don't leave,

939
01:17:48,000 --> 01:17:49,750
I'll blow it up now.

940
01:17:53,917 --> 01:17:57,167
Father, please stop.
We have a lot of money.

941
01:17:57,707 --> 01:17:59,542
Stop causing people problems.

942
01:17:59,875 --> 01:18:01,000
How could you say that?

943
01:18:01,082 --> 01:18:04,000
The money we have today
is because we blow up the stones.

944
01:18:04,082 --> 01:18:05,832
Without it, how will we live?

945
01:18:06,292 --> 01:18:09,375
If you're going to blow it up,
you blow me up too.

946
01:18:09,582 --> 01:18:12,042
My goodness!

947
01:18:12,250 --> 01:18:15,875
Dokkaew, you're acting
as if you're my mother.

948
01:18:16,582 --> 01:18:17,957
Like mother, like daughter.

949
01:18:21,582 --> 01:18:22,625
Where are you going?

950
01:18:24,292 --> 01:18:25,207
Brother.

951
01:18:28,832 --> 01:18:32,792
What are we standing here for?

952
01:18:33,042 --> 01:18:34,875
I don't want to live anymore.

953
01:18:36,250 --> 01:18:37,207
Hey.

954
01:18:38,457 --> 01:18:39,542
Don't go in.

955
01:18:41,082 --> 01:18:44,167
It's dangerous. Come out.

956
01:18:44,292 --> 01:18:46,957
Dokkaew, why are you there with them?
Come out now!

957
01:18:47,542 --> 01:18:50,167
I said come out. It's dangerous.

958
01:18:50,667 --> 01:18:53,207
If it blows,
your head and limbs will be everywhere.

959
01:18:53,500 --> 01:18:57,042
You'll be in many pieces.
It's not pretty. Please come out.

960
01:18:57,542 --> 01:19:00,625
If you don't believe me,
I'll order them to push the button.

961
01:19:03,832 --> 01:19:06,917
I'll really tell them to push the button!

962
01:19:11,250 --> 01:19:12,582
Are you challenging me?

963
01:19:12,917 --> 01:19:15,332
If you don't come out,
I will order them to push the button!

964
01:19:16,582 --> 01:19:19,292
Did you hear? He said to push the button.

965
01:19:20,167 --> 01:19:21,332
How?

966
01:19:21,457 --> 01:19:22,875
This is how.

967
01:19:29,332 --> 01:19:31,207
Why did you do that?
He said five!

968
01:19:31,332 --> 01:19:32,917
I don't know. I already pushed it.

969
01:19:52,375 --> 01:19:54,875
-Please come.
-Don't have to. I'm free.

970
01:20:07,167 --> 01:20:09,417
Dokkaew, where are you?

971
01:20:09,917 --> 01:20:11,750
Buddha, help me!

972
01:20:11,832 --> 01:20:13,167
-You.
-Help!

973
01:20:46,875 --> 01:20:48,000
Completely fine.

974
01:20:48,375 --> 01:20:51,292
Such a big rock.

975
01:20:54,500 --> 01:20:56,292
He's fine.

976
01:20:57,667 --> 01:20:58,832
Hey.

977
01:20:59,457 --> 01:21:04,207
-Brother is fine.
-How come?

978
01:21:05,082 --> 01:21:06,667
Brother is totally fine.

979
01:21:08,750 --> 01:21:10,582
He must have good amulets.

980
01:21:11,125 --> 01:21:13,082
Brother.

981
01:21:16,917 --> 01:21:19,957
Just as I shouted, Buddha, help me!

982
01:21:21,667 --> 01:21:23,957
Hey, guys.

983
01:21:24,707 --> 01:21:25,582
Hey.

984
01:21:26,167 --> 01:21:28,042
Brother is really almighty.

985
01:21:28,375 --> 01:21:31,082
-That's right.
-He can break rocks.

986
01:21:31,332 --> 01:21:34,042
That's right, he's fine.

987
01:21:34,457 --> 01:21:36,250
I didn't do anything.

988
01:21:38,082 --> 01:21:42,125
I was shocked so I froze.

989
01:21:45,000 --> 01:21:46,625
If the rock didn't break,

990
01:21:48,167 --> 01:21:49,832
I'd be dead meat.

991
01:21:50,250 --> 01:21:53,082
No, it must be a miracle.

992
01:21:53,417 --> 01:21:56,250
That's superb. Totally amazing.

993
01:22:08,582 --> 01:22:12,207
Arrest them, they're the culprits.

994
01:22:12,832 --> 01:22:14,332
Arrest them.

995
01:22:15,292 --> 01:22:16,500
There they are.

996
01:22:16,625 --> 01:22:18,000
-Police!
-This is the police. Freeze!

997
01:22:18,167 --> 01:22:19,125
Wait.

998
01:22:19,375 --> 01:22:20,250
Boss.

999
01:22:20,457 --> 01:22:24,707
You're an offender in a contracted
murder case. Take him to the station.

1000
01:22:41,417 --> 01:22:43,375
You're evil.

1001
01:23:05,167 --> 01:23:09,082
The fishes are super fresh.

1002
01:23:09,792 --> 01:23:15,167
BEAUTIFUL VILLAGE BECAUSE
OF OUR UNITED PROJECT

1003
01:23:22,500 --> 01:23:25,957
I think it'd be good
if we have a big school.

1004
01:23:26,082 --> 01:23:28,750
-I think so.
-Our children don't have to travel far.

1005
01:23:28,875 --> 01:23:29,792
They can study here.

1006
01:23:29,875 --> 01:23:33,625
-Different religions studying together?
-Of course, no problem.

1007
01:23:34,000 --> 01:23:37,832
Everybody, today is a ceremony
at our temple.

1008
01:23:38,042 --> 01:23:41,000
Please come together
for the prosperity of the temple.

1009
01:23:41,292 --> 01:23:44,250
Please help.

1010
01:23:44,332 --> 01:23:46,917
The women help check things.

1011
01:23:54,500 --> 01:23:57,125
Our village has so many stories...

1012
01:23:57,875 --> 01:24:00,207
Take all the shells off.

1013
01:24:00,332 --> 01:24:03,542
Do well and I'll teach you English.

1014
01:24:03,792 --> 01:24:06,582
Tan, I speak English fluently now.

1015
01:24:06,667 --> 01:24:09,125
Pig is pig.

1016
01:24:09,582 --> 01:24:10,582
You know?

1017
01:24:12,917 --> 01:24:16,207
Hey. Monk is called monk

1018
01:24:16,500 --> 01:24:18,332
MOBILE DHARMA

1019
01:24:18,457 --> 01:24:22,000
Thanks to Yong's chili paste
which didn't help at all.

1020
01:24:22,125 --> 01:24:23,457
Bought it to eat.

1021
01:24:23,582 --> 01:24:25,332
Mobile Dharma.

1022
01:24:25,542 --> 01:24:27,250
it became Red-Eye chili paste.

1023
01:24:27,375 --> 01:24:29,207
Where to stick "Dharma Car"?

1024
01:24:29,500 --> 01:24:33,292
In front, so people know
it's a monk's car.

1025
01:24:33,500 --> 01:24:35,082
Come together...

1026
01:24:35,207 --> 01:24:38,582
This is "Dharma Car," not monk's car

1027
01:24:38,707 --> 01:24:39,957
You talk too much.

1028
01:24:41,457 --> 01:24:43,832
Come here...

1029
01:24:44,375 --> 01:24:46,667
I invite everyone.

1030
01:24:47,917 --> 01:24:49,292
Please come.

1031
01:24:49,417 --> 01:24:51,792
Who wants to help our temple?

1032
01:24:52,375 --> 01:24:55,082
They say the temple will be good.

1033
01:24:55,582 --> 01:24:57,667
Good morning, Father.

1034
01:24:57,750 --> 01:24:59,167
Full of faith.

1035
01:24:59,457 --> 01:25:02,917
Ever since I met you,
I became so rich.

1036
01:25:04,292 --> 01:25:06,000
Yasothon Rocket Festival.

1037
01:25:06,125 --> 01:25:07,957
I was the only provider.

1038
01:25:08,292 --> 01:25:10,625
If you light my rockets,

1039
01:25:10,750 --> 01:25:13,707
three days and they will
still be up there!

1040
01:25:14,000 --> 01:25:16,542
I don't know if they interrupt the angels.

1041
01:25:16,667 --> 01:25:20,375
I also bring my wife and kid.
Please anoint my wife all over.

1042
01:25:20,500 --> 01:25:21,667
-Bless you.
-Trust me.

1043
01:25:21,832 --> 01:25:24,375
-I'll light it for you.
-You don't have to.

1044
01:25:24,500 --> 01:25:26,707
Count them out, Grandfather.

1045
01:25:26,792 --> 01:25:29,750
Brother, believe me.

1046
01:25:29,917 --> 01:25:32,500
My rockets are top-notch.

1047
01:25:32,625 --> 01:25:35,792
I'll take some with me to light.

1048
01:25:36,000 --> 01:25:39,417
When it goes up, three days,

1049
01:25:39,542 --> 01:25:43,582
it will still be in the sky.

1050
01:25:43,832 --> 01:25:47,292
Make it like a big festival.
I'll take my wife and kid

1051
01:25:47,417 --> 01:25:49,582
for Grandfather to anoint.

1052
01:25:49,667 --> 01:25:51,707
So happy. Grandfather is so fast.

1053
01:26:27,750 --> 01:26:28,917
Grandfather.

1054
01:26:31,332 --> 01:26:33,000
After this ceremony,

1055
01:26:34,625 --> 01:26:36,375
may I visit my mother?

1056
01:26:46,292 --> 01:26:47,500
Father,

